# Lessons Learned

> Append-only log of what worked/failed. Never delete — only compact into archive.
> When file exceeds ~8K tokens, move entries older than 30 days into archive file.
> Format: [DATE] TAG: title — key insight. Link to facts/skills if rule was created.

